    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet required levels across all factors under the Low assurance profile. Monte Carlo UQ on the primary validation study confirms hemolysis index 95th-percentile remains 18% below the clinical threshold. GCI below 5%, iterative convergence confirmed, independent use-error review completed. The assessment panel concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support the VAD hemolysis submission claim under COU2 conditions.",
